Package com.converter.csvconverter.DataBaseHandler

Class SQLHandler

java.lang.Object
com.converter.csvconverter.DataBaseHandler.SQLHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataBaseHandler
@Component public class SQLHandler extends Object implements DataBaseHandler
SQL implementation of the DataBaseHandler interface.

The SQLHandler class implements the methods defined in the DataBaseHandler interface for handling database operations specific to SQL databases. It provides functionality to build DDL statements, batch insert data, create tables, upload data, and configure the SQL database connection.
